For every additional element, why you are adding it
A new separarte database server: A separate server to habnle databse queries exclusively
will greatly add redundancy and remove the SPOF when the application server
is down. Now any query to the database will be more successful regardless of the
states of other servers.

Additional load balancer: To remove the SPOF of having only one load blaancer
anotger is addes to run concurrently or passively with the previous load balancer.